widgets_values:
该组节点的作用：
1、将Controlnet的图像按比例裁切；
2、缩放节点“action”可根据需要选择“裁切”或"扩展"画面；
3、该节点会输出到“Controlnet 图像处理（匹配图像尺寸）”中的选项“1”。

The role of the group of nodes: 
1、 the Controlnet image will be proportionally cropped; 
2、zoom node "action" can be required to select the "crop" or "expand" the screen；
3、the node will be output to the "Controlnet image processing (matching image size)" in the option "1".

该组节点的作用：
1、将Controlnet的图像尺寸进行重新裁剪，使其尺寸与生成图片保持一致；
2、可调整“偏移值”，使其符合生成的图像的预期构图。
3、该节点会输出到“Controlnet 图像处理（匹配图像尺寸）”中的选项“2”。

The role of this group of nodes: 
1. The image size of Controlnet is re-cropped to make its size consistent with the generated image; 
2. The offset value can be adjusted to conform to the expected composition of the generated image.
3、the node will be output to the "Controlnet image processing (matching image size)" in the option "2".

该组节点的作用：
1、将Controlnet的图像尺寸与生成图像尺寸相匹配；
2、根据需要切换“1”或“2”。

The role of this group of nodes: 
1、Match the image size of Controlnet with the size of the generated image; 
2、Switch "1" or "2" as needed.
